task.summary: Improve strength of dim light effect.
Allow to show locus of swiping.
Allow to know path of locus.
Completely change method of collision detection.
Allow to show answer before starting game and to play sequence of Glyphs.
Fix a bug of timing of showing answer.
Allow to edit preference and Change some effects.
Improve effect of flashing on starting game.
Fix a bug on solving question with one shape.
Allow to show remaining time bar.
Allow to show random dot on locus.

MESSAGE.value: Allow to show random dot on locus.
